==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: mantispid
<hw>man*tis"pid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any neuropterous insect of the genus <gen>Mantispa</gen>, and
allied genera. The larvae feed on plant lice. Also used adjectively. See
<xex>Illust.</xex> under <er>Neuroptera</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mantispidae</ent>⟦br⟧
